                     <interp inst="t18470405-939-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> stealing 1 chest, value 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; and 45lbs. weight of tea, 6<hi rend="italic">l</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18470405-name-434" type="victimName">
